      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents about as well as you could hope for. The car is extremely clean inside and out, shows beautifully, and stands out as a truly well-kept, collector-grade vehicle rather than just a nice driver. Cosmetic condition is outstanding, the interior is especially fresh, and overall it gives the impression of a car that has been carefully preserved and properly cared for. A buyer should expect a top-quality example that needs nothing cosmetically and is ready to enjoy, show, or add to a serious collection.",
