    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Priced at $46,900, this vehicle is in mint condition and stands out as an exceptionally well-kept, top-tier example. It runs and drives exactly as it should, presents extremely well inside and out, and shows the kind of care you hope to find in a premium used vehicle. The interior is clean and very well preserved, the exterior shows beautifully, and overall it should meet the expectations of a buyer looking for a turn-key car rather than a project. If you want a vehicle in outstanding condition with little to apologize for, this is a strong one to consider.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Budget-friendly project car offered honestly as a rough example with clear needs. It shows noticeable cosmetic wear inside and out and should be expected to need mechanical sorting before regular use, but it could be a worthwhile option for someone looking for an affordable entry point or a restoration project. If you want something inexpensive and you\u2019re not afraid of putting in work, this one has potential at the right price.",
