      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation. It shows age and wear consistent with a well-used car, but it remains a practical choice for a buyer seeking a low-cost commuter, project, or temporary vehicle. An opportunity to own at a very accessible price point.",
