      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy extra vehicle. Honest sale from someone who knows every used car has a story\u2014this one still has value, and at this price it\u2019s a great chance to get on the road without spending a fortune.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or dependable beater with strong bones and plenty of usable life left. Starts, runs, and moves, with a drivetrain that feels mechanically honest and a chassis that could make a great foundation for a commuter, shop truck, or weekend revival. Not perfect cosmetically and sold as a used vehicle in rough shape, but for the money it offers real utility, straightforward mechanicals, and room to improve without a huge buy-in. Great fit for someone who knows how to turn a wrench and wants an inexpensive platform with potential.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
